🧠 Dissociation (important nuance)

You mentioned it—good catch.

There are two different things:

⚠️ 1. Adaptive Narrowing (good)
	•	tunnel focus
	•	time slows
	•	reduced distraction

👉 Helps performance

⸻

⚠️ 2. Full Dissociation (risky if chronic)
	•	detachment from body/emotion
	•	“not really there” feeling

👉 Useful in extreme moments
👉 Not ideal as a default state

